Wishes:
Generate by a worker in background, shorter text anonymously
Allow files of almost arbitrary size - implement an upload, perhaps convert long (or all?) texts to files

The customizations (e.g. CangJie, Traditional / SImplifiend variant) can be done in CSS only - by hidding the field if undesired.

Separate the words dictionary form the chars.
The dictionary (-ies), can be cached in one HTML file, with a place to insert the mnemonics.

Output variants:
1A epub (word dictionary, character dictionary in separate HTML files, inside one EPUB)
1B portable (a single HTML - the dictionaries have to be merged in)
2A js full preloaded (HTML output - js tooltips (can be loaded from the other file - client side))
2B js preloaded (HTML output - js tooltips, JS annotation client side, dictionary search client side
2C js online  (HTML output - js tooltips, JS annotation client side, (dictionary search and results server side))


